---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for this site: how personal data is handled, plus Cookie, analytics, and advertising disclosures."
>
  <section class="man-section">
    <h2>NAME</h2>
    <p>privacy — Privacy Policy</p>
  </section>

  <section class="man-section">
    <h2>OVERVIEW</h2>
    <p>How this site handles personal information.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="man-section">
    <h2>COLLECTION</h2>
    <p>When you use the contact form, this site may collect the following personal information:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your name</li>
      <li>Your email address</li>
      <li>The content of your inquiry</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Information you provide is used solely to reply to and follow up on your inquiry, and for no
      other purpose. Except where required by law, it is never shared with third parties without
      your consent.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="man-section">
    <h2>THIRD PARTIES</h2>
    <h3>Cookies</h3>
    <p>
      This site uses cookies to improve usability and the site itself. A cookie is a small text file
      a website sends to your browser, used to analyse how the site is used and to serve
      advertising.
    </p>
    <p>
      You can refuse cookies through your browser settings, but some features of the site may not
      work correctly if you do.
    </p>

    <h3>Analytics</h3>
    <p>
      This site uses Google Analytics, a traffic-analysis tool provided by Google. Google Analytics
      uses cookies to collect traffic data. This data is collected anonymously and does not identify
      individuals.
    </p>
    <p>
      You can opt out of this collection by disabling cookies, so please check your browser
      settings. For the Google Analytics terms of service, see the
      <a
        href="https://marketingplatform.google.com/about/analytics/terms/us/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow"
      >
        Google Analytics Terms of Service
      </a>.
    </p>

    <h3>Advertising</h3>
    <p>
      This site uses Google AdSense, a third-party advertising service. Advertising providers may
      use cookies to display ads tailored to your interests.
    </p>
    <p>
      Cookies make it possible to show relevant ads based on your access to this site and others.
    </p>
    <p>
      To disable personalised advertising, change your settings from
      <a
        href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow"
      >
        Google Ad Settings
      </a>. You can also visit
      <a href="https://optout.aboutads.info/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">
        www.aboutads.info
      </a>
      to disable a third-party vendor's cookies used for personalised advertising.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="man-section">
    <h2>RETENTION</h2>
    <h3>Accuracy of information</h3>
    <p>
      I try to provide information that is as accurate as possible, but I do not guarantee its
      accuracy or safety. Please note that information may be outdated or contain errors.
    </p>
    <p>
      I accept no liability for any damages arising from use of the information on this site; please
      use it at your own discretion and risk.
    </p>

    <h3>External links</h3>
    <p>
      This site may contain links to external sites. I take no responsibility for the content or
      services of linked sites. Please use linked sites at your own responsibility after reviewing
      their respective terms.
    </p>

    <h3>Copyright</h3>
    <p>
      Unless otherwise noted, copyright for the articles, images, and other content on this site
      belongs to the site operator. Unauthorised reproduction or copying is prohibited.
    </p>
    <p>When quoting, please cite the source and stay within the bounds of fair quotation.</p>

    <h3>Changes to this policy</h3>
    <p>
      This site may revise this privacy policy as needed. Any changes will be published on this
      page.
    </p>

    <p>Effective date: January 17, 2026</p>
  </section>

  <section class="man-section">
    <h2>CONTACT</h2>
    <p>
      For inquiries about this privacy policy, please reach out via the
      <a href="/contact">contact form</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
